text: Maartje Keuning (born 26 April 1998) is a Dutch water polo player. She plays for the Netherlands women's national water polo team. She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She is a native of Stompetoren. She was educated at OSG Willem Blaeu. She played for University of Hawaii's women's water polo team. and CN Sant Andreu. == References == == Other websites == * Maartje Keuning - Player Info globalsportarchive Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch water polo players
